\left(\cos\frac{\omega}{2}\cos\frac{\alpha+\beta+\omega}{2}\sec\frac{\alpha-\beta}{2},\frac{\csc(\alpha-\beta)}{2}(-\cos\alpha+\cos\beta-\cos(\alpha+\omega)+\cos(\alpha-\beta))\right)
